description:
Merchants that specialize in the sale of camera, film, video, and
other photographic equipment and supplies, including processing
chemicals and papers. Such merchants may or may not also provide
film-processing services.
For merchants that sell camera and video equipment in addition to a
variety of other electronic equipment such as VCRs, televisions, and
stereos, use MCC 5732.
For merchants that primarily provide film processing and printing
services, use MCC 7395.
